Based on the videos and the reading material, what are the ten main components of a report that would be delivered at the end of a data science project? (5 marks)

The videos and reading material observed so far indicate that a data science report should include the following main components:

Cover page
Table of contents
Introductory section
Methodology section
Results section
Discussion section
Conclusion section
References
Acknowledgment
